  "2026-07-18T07:17:36.324Z",codex-sdk-vcs-20260718,"Story tranche evidence 2026-07-18: the VCS acceptance vehicle proves a non-PM domain using only public SDK primitives and includes an itemized GAP_REPORT.md. Every observed primitive need is either complete, explicitly waived as product-specific/bounded, or retained on canonical existing graph/scale lineage; no speculative duplicate SDK items were created. Linked acceptance test passes. The separate temporal digital-twin child pm-kr3t remains open, so this broader story returns to open rather than closing over an active future exemplar."
