  "2026-07-18T15:19:22.552Z",codex-root,"Active acceptance tranche evidence: the pm-vcs exemplar no longer carries its transaction waiver. A package using only public @unbrained/pm-cli/sdk and extension-host services atomically coordinates a Changeset lifecycle transition with an append-only commits_to relationship, including compensation and crash replay. Packed temp install and full VCS flow passed. The separate temporal/business-workflow child remains outside this PR, so this broad story is not being closed by this tranche."
